channel.title: Keldagrim - Where Unique becomes a Reality
channel.description:
[CENTER][img]http://keldagrim.net/imgs/bhead.png[/img] [COLOR=red][size=12pt]Server Developers[/size][/COLOR] [size=12pt]Me | Pasiipaz[/size] [QUOTE][COLOR=red][size=12pt]We plan to take down all those leeches by creating a fun server that has tons of content. Because I know you feel the same way about them as I do, I am tired of seeing the same server over and over in the advertisement section it's time to get a good server in there! Keldagrim is going to be a server that is not easy you will have to work your way to the top. Making money will not be easy like most servers. Getting around will be like runescape. We also understand people come to private servers to pk so we are going to have amazing combat and combat based minigames for people to play.[/size] [/QUOTE][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=red][size=12pt]~ Client Features ~[/size][/COLOR] [COLOR=red][size=12pt]Fixed | Resizeable | Fullscreen | Works in Webclient[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/BdIa0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/NBgH0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/pI3Mh.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Collapsible Inventory and Chat box - Clickable when closed[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/e2MbF.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Long Tabs resized just a little bit[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/mUg7V.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Developers Console[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ZHGuE.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Fully working Summoning orb[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/JdHxc.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/0Sj19.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Xp Orb With multiple icons/ New hitmarks With correct font, Maxhit And Soaking[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/U1L5c.png[/img]
[size=12pt]Quick Prayers - Reset option resets your selected ones | Quick Curses work 100% Also[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/uKTA4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/NnM4b.png[/img] [/COLOR][/CENTER]
[CENTER][COLOR=red][size=12pt]~ Server Features ~[/size][/COLOR] [COLOR=red] [size=12pt]Redoing all skills to be 100% to runescape | Not half assed Summoning Hunter Full Farming Dungeoneering Construction Redone Pvp combat Nazi Zombies Fight Pits Duel Arena Full 63 wave Fight cave Trivia Question Bot Full Dice Bag Pest Control Clan Wars Barrows Npc Pk bot Full Miscellania Fist of Guthix Over 10 Quests | Will go into detail about these later Lootshare and coinshare Clan Chat | Like runescape with ranks promoting demoting ect.. Grand Exchange | As close to Runescape as possible Godwars Good Xp Rate not to slow not to fast Bank Pins Email automated account Recovery System Task System | Hoping to have over 80 Tasks on beta Player Profile information | Not the released one using that as a idea though Deposit all, Deposit Equipment, Deposit BOB | In the bank Full Ancient Curses
Bosses: Jad Tormented Demons Corporeal Beast King Black Dragon Kalphite Queen Nomad Avatar of Destruction Avatar of Creation The Inadequacy THe Everlasting The Untouchable Frost Dragons Balance Elemental Phoenix Bandos Armadyl Sara Kril'[/size] [img]http://i.imgur.com/oqGRD.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/HHFtM.png[/img] [QUOTE][COLOR=red][size=12pt]Any ideas you have please post them here Thanks^^[/COLOR][/QUOTE][/CENTER]
